	[cid] Improve tracing messages; formatting.

2023-05-04  Alexei Podtelezhnikov  <apodtele@gmail.com>

	* src/cache/ftccache.c (ftc_node_hash_unlink): Minor.

2023-05-04  Alexei Podtelezhnikov  <apodtele@gmail.com>

