	Add code to load OT-SVG glyph documents.

	* include/freetype/config/ftheader.h (FT_OTSVG_H): New macro.
	* include/freetype/freetype.h (FT_FACE_FLAG_SVG, FT_HAS_SVG): New macros.
	(FT_LOAD_SVG_ONLY): New internal macro.
