	[builds/windows] Revise MSVC linking optimizations.

	* builds/windows/vc2010/freetype.vcxproj: Optimize DLL linking only.
	* builds/windows/visualc/freetype.dsp: Ditto.
	* builds/windows/visualc/freetype.vcproj: Ditto.

