	Whitespace formatting.

2021-08-22  Alexei Podtelezhnikov  <apodtele@gmail.com>

	Decorate const arguments.

	* src/base/ftglyph.c (FT_Glyph_Transform, FT_Glyph_To_Bitmap): Do it.
